<li id="cite_note-slowcookin-6"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-slowcookin_6-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-slowcookin_6-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text">"One slow-cookin' Trade show". <i><a href="/wiki/The_Globe_and_Mail" title="The Globe and Mail">The Globe and Mail</a></i>, January 31, 1986.</span></li>
